Victoria Beckham took to Instagram to gush over Harper Seven wearing a stunning ball gown as she spends quality time in Italy with her footballer dad. In a snap shared by Victoria, the youngest of her brood could be seen wearing a dazzling, pink and purple ball gown by brand Zimmerman. It comes as Harper and David attended the Riva event at the Fenice theatre. Gushing over the sweet snap of the pair all dressed up, Victoria wrote: "This picture melts my heart. "Special time with the best daddy in the world x Mummy loves you both so much. "You are my everything @davidbeckham kisses #harperseven," she penned alongside a row of purple hearts.